Package: ugrthesisdown
Title: An updated R Markdown thesis template using the bookdown package
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Chester", "Ismay", email = "chester.ismay@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut")),
    person("Nick", "Solomon", email = "nick@nicksolomon.me", role = "aut"),
    person("Antonio J","Pérez-Luque",  email = "ajpelu@gmail.com", role =c("cre", "aut")))
Description: Using the bookdown and thesisdown packages, and custom templates from
    Univeristy of Granada, this package aims to encourage reproducible research using
    simple Markdown syntax while embedding all of the R code to produce plots
    and analyses as well.
Maintainer: Antonio J. Pérez-Luque <ajpelu@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    bookdown,
    knitr,
    here
Suggests:
    remotes,
    usethis
